<section class='section-actions container'>
<div class='row'>
<div class='col-md-3 col-xs-6 boxed-content browse'>
<a href='/browse_data'>
<i class='flaticon-database'></i>
</a>
<h2 class='boxed-content-title'>Browse database</h2>
<p>
Browse and query more than 100 thousand trait scores, and
look for related QTLs in a variety of Brassica subspicies.
</p>
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/browse_data">Browse data</a>
</div>
<div class='col-md-3 col-xs-6 boxed-content submit'>
<a href='/submissions/new'>
<i class='flaticon-pages'></i>
</a>
<h2 class='boxed-content-title'>Submit new data</h2>
<p>
Submit your experimental Brassica population data along with scored
traits and identified genetic mappings to be published in the Portal.
</p>
<a class="btn btn-action" href="/submissions/new">Submit data</a>
</div>
<div class='col-md-3 col-xs-6 boxed-content analyse'>
<a href='/analyses/new'>
<i class='flaticon-magnifier'></i>
</a>
<h2 class='boxed-content-title'>Analyse data</h2>
<p>
Perform genome-wide association study to identify genetic variants
underpinning phenotypic trait variability.
</p>
<a class="btn btn-accent-3" href="/analyses/new">Perform analysis</a>
</div>
<div class='col-md-3 col-xs-6 boxed-content documentation'>
<a href='/api_documentation'>
<i class='flaticon-settings'></i>
</a>
<h2 class='boxed-content-title'>API Documentation</h2>
<p>
Learn how to integrate your own software with our Portal in order to
automatically retrieve and submit large quantities of data.
</p>
<a class="btn btn-mono" href="/api_documentation">API documentation</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
